dex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104asq1665702609631.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/asq1665702609631.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/asq1665702609631.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"asq1665702609631\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Horizontal Alignment\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Horizontal alignment of the label—<code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Center</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"asq1665702609631__section_w1837ab1b5b1_w1838ab1b5_w1839ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__2\">Representation</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__2\">\n (Default)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__3\">If not specified, the label is\n                        left-aligned</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">L</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__3\">Label is left-aligned</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Center</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__3\">Label is centered; appropriate for tabular\n                        layouts</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">R</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"asq1665702609631__table_d12971e1_d12972e1_d12973e1__entry__3\">Label is right-aligned</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"asq1665702609631__section_anh_xdk_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865076e152\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"asq1665702609631__p_d109940e1_d109941e1_d109942e1\">This property can be set only via the pop-up menu\n            on a label.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"asq1665702609631__section_dsf_ydk_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865076e161\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"asq1665702609631__p_d109922e1_d109923e1_d109924e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngv1688454370143.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngv1688454370143.html\" title=\"A label displays text on a component, such as the name of an associated field or an instruction to the user.\">Label</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702614021.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Labels in Forms and Reports</a><p>Labels are objects that contain static. Most labels are associated with a field, but unassociated labels can be used for any static text on the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611989\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611989\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Horizontal Alignment Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Horizontal Alignment Horizontal alignment of the label— Left , Right , or Center . Value Representation Description (Default) If not specified, the label is left-aligned L Left Label is left-aligned C Center Label is centered; appropriate for tabular layouts R Right Label is right-aligned Description This property can be set only via the pop-up menu on a label. Applies To Label Related Links Labels in Forms and Reports Labels are objects that contain static. Most labels are associated with a field, but unassociated labels can be used for any static text on the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}